程序包 org.janusgraph.core.util

类 JanusGraphId

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.core.util.JanusGraphId
@Deprecated
public class JanusGraphId
extends Object
已过时。
This class does not produce valid JanusGraph vertex ids as it does not take into account partitioning bits used in vertex id assignment. Use IDManager, which can be obtained through StandardJanusGraph.getIDManager() and includes methods for converting a user id to (IDManager.toVertexId(long)) and from (IDManager.fromVertexId(long)) JanusGraph vertex id. 

 IDManager idManager = ((StandardJanusGraph) graph).getIDManager();
Utility methods for handling JanusGraph ids and converting them between indexing and storage backend representations.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)

  • 方法详细资料

    • toVertexId

      public static long toVertexId​(long id)
      已过时。
      Use IDManager.toVertexId(long).
      Converts a user provided long id into a JanusGraph vertex id. The id must be positive and can be at most 61 bits long. This method is useful when providing ids during vertex creation via Graph.addVertex(Object...).
      参数:
      id - long id
      返回:
      a corresponding JanusGraph vertex id

    • fromVertexId

      public static long fromVertexId​(long id)
      已过时。
      Use IDManager.fromVertexId(long)
      Converts a JanusGraph vertex id to the user provided id as the inverse mapping of toVertexId(long).
      参数:
      id - JanusGraph vertex id (must be positive)
      返回:
      original user provided id

    • fromVertexID

      public static long fromVertexID​(JanusGraphVertex v)
      已过时。
      Use IDManager.fromVertexId(long)
      Converts a JanusGraph vertex id of a given vertex to the user provided id as the inverse mapping of toVertexId(long).
      参数:
      v - Vertex
      返回:
      original user provided id
